SUMMARY: Acoustic Saturday at Adobe Road Winery featuring Jeremy Gorman
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a special Saturday acoustic live music set at Ado
 be Road Winery in downtown Petaluma. Sip on award-winning wines while enj
 oying talented local musicians in a warm and inviting atmosphere. Choose 
 from wines by the glass or bottle to discover new favorites. Reserve your
  spot on Tock https://www.exploretock.com/adoberoadwines/ and make it a m
 emorable night of great music\, fine wine\, and good company!\n\nAbout Je
 remy Gorman\n\nFor San Francisco Bay Area multi-instrumentalist\, Jeremy 
 Gorman\, music has been nothing short of a lifetime journey of self-expre
 ssion and self-realization. Currently performing as a solo artist\, Jerem
 y has collaborated with many bands around the North Bay area\, including 
 a project titled spaceMüs with daughter\, Blair Gorman.\n\nWith a deep kn
 owledge of music theory\, along with a vast range of musical tastes\, Jer
 emy creates story-driven songs that capture ideas of hope and gratitude\,
  and of his own personal life’s journey.
CATEGORIES:music,live-music,wine,winery
