SUMMARY: Sunday Sessions with "Fire Up!"
DESCRIPTION:Griffo is excited to welcome Fire Up!\, a Bay Area Tribute to
  the Garcia Saunders Songbook. This rotating cast of players will have yo
 u transported with the first tune. Bodega Market Deli will be serving up 
 food all day while the Griffo crew serves up delicious cocktails from our
  ever rotating menu! Don't miss this homage to an era of music that never
  goes out of style!\n\nSee you Sundays!\n\n\nWho's Playing: Fire Up!\n\nW
 ho's Cooking: Bodega Market Deli\n\nWhen: Sunday\, March 15th - Doors @ 1
  pm\n\nWhere: Griffo Distillery\n\nPlease RSVP for this FREE\, All Ages E
 vent. Space is Limited.\n\n\nAbout the Band:\n\nFire up! Is a tribute ban
 d interpreting the Jerry Garcia “Legion of Mary” era. Fire Up! is branded
  as “Songs from the Garcia – Saunders songbook."\n\nFor note\, Fire Up! i
 s a name of a Garcia Saunders studio album\, open.spotify.com/album/2b85g
 bWiMbAg3cvSUTMIBp https://open.spotify.com/album/2b85gbWiMbAg3cvSUTMIBp\n
 \nOur project is funky\, bluesy\, Jamy\, RnB\, and Jazzy with an emphasis
  on the Hammond organ. One might say “Ballroom brawling\, baby making mus
 ic" modeled after the 1972 – 1975 Legion of Mary era. It is different tha
 n what you hear from other JGB bands who focus on more of the 80’s and 90
 ’s gospel Jerry era.
CATEGORIES:music,concert,griffo,livemusic
