SUMMARY: Opening Reception: Quiet Structure by Roberta Ahrens
DESCRIPTION:What: Quiet Structure + Opening Reception\n\nWhen: Opening Re
 ception - Saturday\, April 4th\, 2025\, 5 - 8 pm\, Show Run - March 24th 
 - April 26th\n\nLocation: Usher Gallery\, 1 Petaluma Blvd North\, Petalum
 a\n\n"Quiet Structure" showcases a selection of contemporary botanical an
 d water-based works by Roberta Ahrens.\n\nRoberta Ahrens is a California-
 based artist whose practice centers on contemporary works created on hand
 made cracked linen. This featured exhibition will be on view at Usher Gal
 lery from March 24th to April 26th.\n\nJoin us for the opening reception 
 to enjoy live music by Sophia Rayne\, refreshments\, and an opportunity t
 o meet and connect with the artist.\n\nArtist Statement:\n\n"I create con
 temporary botanical and water-based works on my own handmade cracked line
 n. The surface is my primary collaborator built\, fractured\, carved\, an
 d layered with\nacrylic\, watercolor\, and clay base until it holds both 
 structure and light.\nI’m drawn to what I think of as nature’s architectu
 re: the way a petal opens like a vault\, the way water forms strata throu
 gh movement and pressure. Rather than simply depicting flowers or waves\,
  I interpret them in a wider artistic landscape.\nScale matters. Many pie
 ces are meant to be experienced bodily\, and emotionally\, ways that reve
 al subtle shifts in depth and translucency as light moves across them.\nW
 ith both botanicals and water\, I pursue a shared language of balance and
  motion where stillness and force exist at the same time. My intention is
  to offer a place to slow down and feel the quiet intelligence of the nat
 ural world."\n\n- Roberta Ahrens\n\nMore details about Roberta Ahrens and
  her work can be found at: https://www.robertaahrens.com/ https://www.rob
 ertaahrens.com/
CATEGORIES:
X-TKF-FEATURED-IMAGE:https://d3flpus5evl89n.cloudfront.net/5e1e2fe9df82fe
 0e2d29328c/69cab228dc7c9e8f45bcebe2/scaled_1024.jpg
X-TKF-CUSTOM-PREVIEW:What: Quiet Structure + Opening Reception When: Open
 ing Reception - Saturday\, April 4th\, 2025\, 5 - 8 pm\, Show Run - March
  24th - April 26th Location:...
LOCATION:Usher Gallery Petaluma\,1 Petaluma Boulevard North\, Petaluma\, 
 CA 94952\, USA
