SUMMARY: Thursday Live Music with Michelle Lambert at Adobe Road Winery
DESCRIPTION:Join us Thursday night for indoor live music at Adobe Road Wi
 nery! Sip on award-winning wines while enjoying talented local musicians 
 in a warm and inviting atmosphere. Choose from wines by the glass or bott
 le and discover new favorites. Reserve your spot on Tock https://www.expl
 oretock.com/adoberoadwines/ and make it a memorable night of great music\
 , fine wine\, and good company!\n\nRising star\, Michelle Lambert https:/
 /www.michellelambert.com/ \, brings a world of experience when she steps 
 up to the microphone. This Pop singer/songwriter has toured from coast to
  coast making waves all over the country from the Great American Music Ha
 ll in San Francisco to the Bridgestone Arena in Nashville. Michelle’s 202
 1 single\, Come to Me\, has caught the attention of the press and reached
  #1 on Indie Radio for 4 consecutive weeks.
