SUMMARY: UltraBomb with Boss' Daughter + Redwood Chrome
DESCRIPTION:Legendary punk supergroup UltraBomb is hitting WonderStump on
  their 2026 North American tour! Catch songs from their new record\, Look
  Forward In Anger\, live and loud. This is your chance to experience the 
 sound of genre-shaping musicians in a venue built for close-up\, immersiv
 e shows.\n\nUltraBomb is comprised of punk rock veterans: Greg Norton (Hü
 sker Dü) — bass\, vocals • Derek O’Brien (Social Distortion\, Agent Orang
 e\, Adolescents) — drums\, vocals • Ryan Smith (Soul Asylum) — guitar\, v
 ocals\n\nJoining them are Boss' Daughter straight out of Reno\, and homet
 own heroes Redwood Chrome.\n\nDoors open at 6 ⎸ This is a 21+ event. Vali
 d ID required for entry.
CATEGORIES:Live-music,punk-rock,punk
