SUMMARY: Petaluma Downtown Sidewalk Sale
DESCRIPTION:The annual Petaluma Downtown Sidewalk Sale will take place Th
 ursday\, July 30 - Sunday\, August 2\, 2026.\n\nIndependent stores and re
 staurants are a vital part of the special character of Downtown Petaluma.
  The Sidewalk Sale is a perfect opportunity to do your part in keeping Pe
 taluma retail alive and take home some great items at a fraction of the c
 ost!\n\nJoin us for a stroll\, grab a coffee\, lunch\, and enjoy a fun sh
 opping experience at the Downtown Summer Sidewalk Sale!\n\nVisit petaluma
 downtown.com https://petalumadowntown.com/petaluma-sidewalk-sale-marketpl
 ace for a list of participating merchants.
