SUMMARY: Petaluma Fall Antique Faire
DESCRIPTION:Petaluma Fall Antique Faire\n\nThe much-anticipated Petaluma 
 Fall Antique Faire returns on September 27\, from 8am to 4pm\, in Histori
 c Downtown Petaluma. The Faire is located on Western Ave\, the A Street P
 arking lot\, and 4th & Kentucky Streets between B Street and Washington S
 treet.\n\n"The Bay Area's Premier Antique Center\," Historic Downtown Pet
 aluma will transform into an antique marketplace. Amid the beautiful hist
 oric buildings\, one-of-a-kind stores\, an incredible array of restaurant
 s and cafes\, guests can find an incomparable selection of affordable ant
 iques from over 200 dealers. The show has a fantastic variety of estate j
 ewelry\, linens\, furniture\, art\, kitchenware\, vintage décor\, books\,
  and all kinds of unusual collectibles to suit everyone's budget.\n\nAnti
 que and collectible lovers throughout the Bay Area are welcome to browse 
 and shop the 40th Annual Petaluma Antique Faire set in our delightful and
  relaxing downtown Petaluma.\n\nThis show attracts over 8k discerning col
 lectors as well as first-time buyers wishing to collect and invest in rea
 l antiques.\n\nVisit http://petalumadowntown.com\n\n~ Admission is free ~
